<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />

    <title>SHIF Calculator Kenya | Calculate SHIF Contributions Online</title>

    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Free Kenya SHIF Calculator. Calculate your Social Health Insurance Fund (SHIF) contribution instantly using the latest Kenya SHIF rates. Fast, accurate, and easy to use."
    />

    <meta
      name="keywords"
      content="SHIF Calculator Kenya, Kenya SHIF Calculator, Social Health Insurance Fund Calculator, SHIF contribution calculator, Kenya payroll calculator"
    />

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <link rel="canonical" href="https://yourdomain.com/shif-calculator" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>

  <body data-api-url="<%= API_URL %>">
    <%- include('../shared/header') %>

    <main>
      <section>
        <h1>Kenya SHIF Calculator</h1>

        <p>
          As an employee, your employer will deduct this SHIF and remit it to
          Social Health Authority (SHA) on your behalf through KRA Online
          Portal. Social Health Insurance Fund (SHIF) is Kenya’s national health
          insurance scheme that replaced NHIF as part of the Universal Health
          Coverage (UHC) reforms. It is mandatory for all Kenyan residents,
          whether formally employed, self-employed, or unemployed. Contributions
          are income-based, calculated as a fixed percentage of gross income,
          ensuring higher earners contribute more while expanding coverage for
          lower-income groups through government support.
        </p>

        <h2>SHIF Rates</h2>

        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Gross Monthly Income (KES)</th>
              <th>SHIF Contribution (KES)</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>

          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>KES 0 - KES 5,999</td>
              <td>KES 300</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>KES 6,000 and above</td>
              <td>2.75% of gross salary</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section id="shif-form-section">
        <form id="shif-form" autocomplete="off">
          <h2>SHIF Calculator</h2>

          <div>
            <label for="gross-pay">Gross Monthly Salary (KES)</label>
            <input
              id="gross-pay"
              name="grossPay"
              type="number"
              placeholder="0.00"
              min="0"
              step="0.01"
              required
            />
          </div>

          <p id="error-message" hidden></p>

          <button type="submit">Calculate</button>
        </form>
      </section>

      <section id="results" hidden aria-live="polite">
        <div class="results-success">
          <p id="success-message"></p>
        </div>

        <h2>Results</h2>

        <table>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Gross Salary</td>
              <td id="gross-salary">KES 0.00</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>SHIF</strong></td>
              <td id="shif"><strong>KES 0.00</strong></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <button id="reset-btn">Reset</button>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('../shared/footer') %>

    <script src="/js/shif.js" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
